Package robot

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Button
    Handles the Lego EV3 Touch Sensor.
    Data
    Initializes the connection between the EV3 and a PC for communication between the devices and transmiting data.
    Motors
    Handles the Lego EV3 motors and their movements.
    Play
    The main loop that initializes the whole program and commences the behavior performance.
    Pressing
    The behavior for which handles the situation in which the touch sensor is pressed while the motors aren't moving.
    RobotsTurn
    The behavior which handles moving the chess pieces.
    Stop
    The behavior which handles the situation in which the touch sensor is pressed for emergency stop while the motors are moving.
    Waiting
    This is the lowest priority behavior which will be in action while all the other behaviors are being suppressed.
